message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper discusses the development of a pipeline for visualizing uncertainty and saliency maps of deep convolutional neural networks for medical imaging applications. This involves the use of computer vision techniques (cs.CV) and machine learning algorithms (cs.LG, cs.AI) to analyze medical images (cs.MED) and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
